name: Just can't prove it
description: The DETECTIVE token represents the viral meme of the TV show detective Doakes that's always on to something but can not seem to prove what's happening. The meme has started to pick up traction in April and has recently accelerated in virality, with some tweets exceeding 20 million views. The token is all about connecting those who enjoy the meme and making fun memes about it together. It's a memecoin.
